    "title": "GSAP ScrollTrigger",
    "description": "Minimal two-row layout demonstrating smooth scroll-tied text and box reveal using GSAP ScrollTrigger with scrub smoothing. Clean, dependency-lite, and ready to embed.",
    "code": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>GSAP Text Reveal â€¢ Glossy White Demo</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Minimal GSAP ScrollTrigger text reveal on a modern glossy white background\" />\n  \n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --ink: #0f172a;\n      --ink-muted: #475569;\n      --border: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);\n      --radius: 14px;\n      --space-16: 4rem;\n      --maxw: 1000px;\n    }\n\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body { height: 100%; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\";\n      color: var(--ink);\n      background: #fff;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n    }\n\n    main { max-width: var(--maxw); margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-16) 1rem var(--space-16); }\n\n    .row { margin-top: var(--space-16); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; }\n\n    /* Elements that reveal */\n    .reveal { transform: translateY(40px) translateZ(0); opacity: 0; will-change: transform, opacity; }\n    .text { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; color: var(--ink-muted); }\n\n    /* Visual box placeholder */\n    .box { aspect-ratio: 16 / 10; width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #f5f7fb; }\n\n    /* (typography/footer rules removed) */\n\n    @media (max-width: 900px) { .row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <main>\n    <!-- Row 1: text + box (minimal) -->\n    <section class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"text reveal\">\n        <h2>Text reveal</h2>\n        <p>Content block rises and fades in as you scroll.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"box reveal\"></div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Row 2: box + text (minimal) -->\n    <section class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"box reveal\"></div>\n      <div class=\"text reveal\">\n        <h2>Another block</h2>\n        <p>Mirrored layout with the same smooth reveal.</p>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/gsap.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\"></script>\n  <script>\n    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n    // Animate each reveal element with scrub smoothing for consistent motion\n    gsap.utils.toArray('.reveal').forEach((el) => {\n      const tl = gsap.timeline({\n        scrollTrigger: {\n          trigger: el,\n          start: 'top 85%',\n          end: 'top 35%',\n          scrub: 0.8, // smoothing so fast or slow scroll feels consistent\n          toggleActions: 'play none none reverse',\n          invalidateOnRefresh: true\n        }\n      });\n\n      tl.to(el, { y: 0, opacity: 1, ease: 'none' });\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
  }
